{"tid":169206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大生考試放屁 被扣10分","createTime":"2017-03-24T05:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T22:13:38.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10a664003b72bb55adab4d7bb426b7c3389b8b61","tid":169206,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170324/large/1490331308_b04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F1490331308_b04b.jpg&h=639946be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有科大學生在網上爆料稱，一名就讀「環境科學學科」的學生，在三月十八日參加課程「Introduction to Atmospheric Science」中期考試時，因為放了三次屁，而被其他考生投訴，該課程教授其後向該名放屁學生發電郵，稱這樣做會產生臭味和騷擾他人，所以決定扣他十分。最後，教授更叮囑該名考生，要多吃蔬菜和水果。 <br />\n<br />\n本刊已向科大求證，未獲最終回覆，但表示多間傳媒都在查問。"},{"pid":"bf5d9f34b6039419c056e641e11329849ea4f2cc","tid":169206,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397ae9700ced912cc6b7110a319a721ab18f330f","tid":169206,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"某些人體味大要唔要扣分先？"},{"pid":"d9ae9b5b94b6081c17e176a5739642239ee7400f","tid":169206,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"讀環境科學竟然放屁破壞環境梗要罰"},{"pid":"92a9ae09edfb31806f103147728a1a7b4ecd9cd3","tid":169206,"uid":43302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89614b6042a31a5b963a249a9191dda54bb093d4","tid":169206,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:50:34.